99
00:09:42,214 --> 00:09:45,284
-I'm a stockbroker.
-Stockbroker. Oh, goodness.

100
00:09:45,618 --> 00:09:47,687
Had to go to college
to be a stockbroker, huh?

101
00:09:47,820 --> 00:09:51,657
