after work.

110
00:10:49,749 --> 00:10:52,985
-For what?
-I wanna see about a job there.

111
00:10:53,119 --> 00:10:55,855
Yeah? What job?

112
00:10:56,222 --> 00:10:58,290
You know, when I--

113
00:10:58,424 --> 00:11:01,193
When I was a kid, I could go through
a math book in a week.

114
00:11:01,327 --> 00:11:04,764
So I'm gonna go see about
what job they got down there.

115
00:11:05,831 --> 00:11:07,800
What job?

116
00:11:10,770 --> 00:11:12,371
Stockbroker.

117
00:11:14,774 --> 00:11:17,977
-Stockbroker?
-Yeah.

118
00:11:18,277 --> 00:11:20,312
Not an astronaut?

