131
00:12:16,936 --> 00:12:19,472
This is what I'm trying to do
for my family...

132
00:12:19,805 --> 00:12:21,173
...for you and for Christopher.

133
00:12:22,508 --> 00:12:24,810
What's the matter with you?

134
00:12:28,914 --> 00:12:30,516
Linda.

135
00:12:31,117 --> 00:12:32,785
Linda.

136
00:12:59,545 --> 00:13:04,884
This part of my life
is called "Being Stupid."

137
00:13:06,886 --> 00:13:08,154
Can I ask you a favor, miss?

138
00:13:08,287 --> 00:13:12,158
Do you mind if I leave this here
with you just for five minutes?

139
00:13:12,291 --> 00:13:14,994
I have a meeting in there
and I don't wanna carry that...

140
00:13:15,127 --> 00:13:17,163
...looking smalltime.

141
00:13:17,963 --> 00:13:22,368
Here is a dollar and I'll give you
more money when I come back out.

142
00:13:22,501 --> 00:13:25,938
Okay? It's not valuable.
You can't sell it anywhere.

143
00:13:26,872 --> 00:13:31,544
I can't even sell it, and it's my job.
All right? Be right back.

144
00:13:38,551 --> 00:13:41,053
-Chris? Tim Brophy, Resources.
-Yes. How are you?

145
00:13:41,187 --> 00:13:42,488
-Follow me.
