-Good morning.

225
00:19:44,349 --> 00:19:45,751
-Mr. Twistle, Chris Gardner.
-Hi.

226
00:19:45,884 --> 00:19:48,687
I wanted to drop this off personally
and make your acquaintance.

227
00:19:48,820 --> 00:19:52,457
